  <entry>
    <title>virtual host pada xampp di windows</title>
    <link href="http://buqento.com/2018/09/23/virtual-host-pada-xampp-di-windows/"/>
    <id>http://buqento.com/2018/09/23/virtual-host-pada-xampp-di-windows/</id>
    <published>2018-09-23T01:00:10.000Z</published>
    <updated>2018-09-23T03:53:38.182Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Menambahkan-domain-baru"><a href="#Menambahkan-domain-baru" class="headerlink" title="Menambahkan domain baru"></a>Menambahkan domain baru</h2><p>Buka direktori C:\Windows\System32\drivers\etc, kemudian buka “hosts” menggunakan editor (notepad atau yang lainnya). Tambahkan domain baru dengan menambahkan perintah berikut.</p><figure class="highlight plain"><figcaption><span>host</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line">127.0.0.1   frontend.vms</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><a id="more"></a><h2 id="Menambahkan-data-virtual-host"><a href="#Menambahkan-data-virtual-host" class="headerlink" title="Menambahkan data virtual host"></a>Menambahkan data virtual host</h2><p>Langkah selanjutnya adalah menambahkan virtual host. Buka direktori C:\xampp\apache\conf\extra. Kemudian buka file httpd-vhosts.conf dengan notepad. Tambahkan virtual host baru seperti blok kode berikut.</p><figure class="highlight plain"><figcaption><span>httpd-vhosts.conf</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line">&lt;VirtualHost *:80&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    ServerName frontend.vms</span><br><span class="line">    DocumentRoot &quot;C:/xampp/htdocs/vms/frontend/web/&quot;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;Directory &quot;C:/xampp/htdocs/vms/frontend/web/&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">        RewriteEngine on</span><br><span class="line">        RewriteCond %&#123;REQUEST_FILENAME&#125; !-f</span><br><span class="line">        RewriteCond %&#123;REQUEST_FILENAME&#125; !-d</span><br><span class="line">        RewriteRule . index.php</span><br><span class="line">        DirectoryIndex index.php</span><br><span class="line">        Require all granted</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;/Directory&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/VirtualHost&gt;</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Pada contoh ini, nama virtual host adalah frontend.vms, dengan document root C:/xampp/htdocs/vms/frontend/web/.</p><h2 id="Uji-coba"><a href="#Uji-coba" class="headerlink" title="Uji coba"></a>Uji coba</h2><p>Untuk melakukan uji coba, jalankan apache service melalui XAMPP control panel. Kemudian buka web browser (mozila atau google chrome) dengan mengetikan alamat virtual host (frontend.vms) yang telah dibuat.</p><img src="/2018/09/23/virtual-host-pada-xampp-di-windows/uji.jpg" title="Virtual host">]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;h2 id=&quot;Menambahkan-domain-baru&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#Menambahkan-domain-baru&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;Menambahkan domain baru&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Menambahkan domain baru&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Buka direktori C:\Windows\System32\drivers\etc, kemudian buka “hosts” menggunakan editor (notepad atau yang lainnya). Tambahkan domain baru dengan menambahkan perintah berikut.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight plain&quot;&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;span&gt;host&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;...&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;127.0.0.1   frontend.vms&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;...&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
    
